property.name: note
property.value:
Segement 1 will loop when Intensity and Intensity 2 are both 0 Value
Playhead will jump to Segment 2 when Intensity is at the min value of 1 and will stay between 1 and 2
Section 2 will loop as long a the intensity meters stay between 1 and 2
Anxiety drums will start to fade when the intensity is between 1 and 2 and the anxiety meter is at min of 56% - Drums will kick in when Anxiety meters is at 32% - This will loop until the anxiety meter returns back to 100%
IMPORTANT - For the anxiety meter to kick in you need the intensity to remain between 1 and 2 otherwise it will not function.
